text.text:
100% recommend cakes from here!

When I arrived to collect my cake, there was miscommunication as I had requested a change of date over a month prior but this had not been noted down on my order so there was no cake for my sons birthday when I turned up, but this was amazingly turned around.

The reason I give 5 stars is due to the fact it was an honest mistake and rather than making excuses, the lady made me a spiderman cake within only a few hours and offered to give me some money back also.

I refused the money as she really went in to superhero mode to get this cake made and her customer service was absolutely amazing, she deserved every penny she charged for that cake  and I will be going back to her for future orders.

I could tell she puts her heart and soul into her cakes and delivering excellent customer service.

I believe the young lady is called Demi, I would like to thank her for turning a potential stressful issue into an amazing result, the cake turned out better than I imagined and was the highlight of my sons birthday.

Thank you CAKE MAGIC 🙌🏼

I refused the money as she really went in to superhero mode to get this cake made and her customer service was absolutely amazing, she deserved every penny she charged for that cake  and I will be going back to her for future orders.

I could tell she puts her heart and soul into her cakes and delivering excellent customer service.

I believe the young lady is called Demi, I would like to thank her for turning a potential stressful issue into an amazing result, the cake turned out better than I imagined and was the highlight of my sons birthday.

Thank you CAKE MAGIC 🙌🏼
